				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \mathrm{PTR}=\mathbbm{I}\left\{\mu \left(A=1/2,Z\right)-\mu \left(A=-1/2,Z\right)>0\right\} $$\end{document}PTR=IμA=1/2Z−μA=−1/2Z>0

